sokochan

Class SokochanEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • sokochan.SokochanEngine

  • public final class SokochanEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    This class organises all the other core classes of the Sokoban engine. The parsing of levels has been implemented here, but the loading from files is developed in the MapLoader Class.

    Created by Vittorio on 05-Oct-16.
